      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a definitive example of the E46 M3, maintained to a standard that exceeds factory requirements. The S54B32 power unit features a recently overhauled VANOS system with Beisan components and a comprehensive valve adjustment. Power is delivered through the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a 3.62 limited-slip differential, ensuring linear torque delivery. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring proactive rear subframe reinforcement and fresh RTABs. The suspension utilizes Bilstein dampers tuned for the original spring rates, preserving the OEM+ handling profile. The exterior displays factory-consistent paint thickness with no orange peel or oxidation, while the cabin retains its original matte finish on all touchpoints. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast.",
